title: Rito, let's talk tank meta

embed.description: So I wanna discuss this current tanky meta that includes tanks or squishy assassins that just build into tanks. This is my breakdown of why they are so strong. But you need to split these tanks into two groups, one being actual tanks, the other being assassin tanks.

body: Let's break down why tank meta is SO annoying currently. Last year tank meta didn't even bother me, i loved it, but this year is so much worse and heres why.
